      "description": "Available now is a meticulously curated example of precision engineering, maintained to an exacting standard that exceeds factory specifications. This chassis remains remarkably rigid, benefiting from a comprehensive suspension refresh featuring polyurethane bushings and corner-balanced coilovers for optimal weight distribution. Under the hood, the powerplant exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with a top-end rebuild that addressed common VANOS concerns and high-pressure fuel rail tolerances. The drivetrain is exceptionally tight, with zero lash in the differential and crisp engagement through every gate of the short-throw shifter. This isn't just a driver; it's a turn-key performance machine with a pristine undercarriage and a paint depth that confirms it has lived a pampered, climate-controlled life. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade specimen.",
